{
  "stem": "3988.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We all lived in a small town, very small town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't-- same thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They couldn't do nothing because they were, you know, under occupation too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they-- they didn't do too much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then after I worked in town-- and I don't know how many months-- so I went to work-- to work on a farm.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father, my mother said I'd be safer to work on the farm, which the farm was in walking distance, not-- not too far.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I worked there five, six days a week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the farms-- would take the cows out to the field, you know, and watch them in the pasture.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because there were no fences.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Other farmers had land too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they didn't want the cows to go, you know, on their land.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had to watch them, they shouldn't cross to somebody else's land.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I used to watch them and from morning, early morning, till late at night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I used to bring home-- and then I used to clean the stables, you know, put fresh straw down, and feed them, you know, and clean them up, and work, whatever I had to do, work on the farm.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And sleep, I slept on a-- on a-- hay, a loft, you know, what you would call a loft, where you keep the hay stacked up in the barn.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Used to have a ladder, go up on the lofts, sleep there on the-- on the hay.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was some farmer's.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Polish, Polish farmer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for work on the farm, I used to go home on Sunday, get a couple hours off on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he pay me with bread, or milk, or eggs.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
